Package: opencis
Type: Package
Title: Import Data from Spanish Sociological Research Center (CIS)
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Héctor Meleiro
Maintainer: Héctor Meleiro <hmeleiro@gmail.com>
Description: Search and import data directly to R from the [Spanish Sociological Research Center (CIS)](https://www.cis.es/inicio).
    The CIS is a public institution that conducts electoral and sociological research studies on the Spanish society. 
    The CIS has a large database of surveys that can be accessed through its website. The package includes functions 
    to search for surveys, survey questions and timeseries, and import the data directly to R.
